-- Telecom Italia May Revamp Control of Latin American Units, Messaggero Says
-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2010-10-15T05:48:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/telecom-italia-may-revamp-control-of-latin-american-units-messaggero-says.html
Telecom Italia SpA  may reorganize
the chain of control of its businesses in Argentina and Brazil,
daily Il Messaggero reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Telecom Italia may also increase its investments in
Argentina, according to the Italian newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
